!'''Label'''
!'''Rail Type'''
|-
|RAIL 
| Normal Rail
|-
|ELRL 
| Electrified Rail
|-
|MONO 
| Mono Rail
|-
|MGLV 
| Maglev Rail
|}

{{en/Ottdp|1.0|no|ottdrev=r18969}} 16 railtypes can be defined.

{{en/Ottdp|1.9|no|ottdrev=bf8d7df7}} 64 railtypes can be defined.

Zestawy typów szyn mogą wykorzystywać do 64 rodzajów szyn i muszą określać własne [[pl/Development/NewGRF/NFO Specs/TracktypeLabels|etykiety]].

See also [[en/Action0/Global Settings#rail-type-translation-table-12|Rail Type Translation Table]] for further info.

